&lt;p&gt;Job summary&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have an exciting opportunity for a radiographer to join our team in Jersey. Jersey is situated in the English Channel and it boasts many local Heritage sites and some of the world’s finest beaches. Due to the mild climate walking, cycling, numerous water sports and many other outdoor pursuits are all on your doorstep. It is a very safe island for families. The successful applicant must have experience in General X Ray and MRI and participation in the General X Ray on call system is required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We undertake a wide range of imaging examinations. We are QSI accredited which brings many opportunities and we aim to deliver excellent patient care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A relocation package is available to successful off island applicants.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like an informal discussion about the role, please send your telephone number by email to Nicola King on n.king@health.gov.jeand tell us when it is best for us to call you back.&lt;/p&gt;
